Title: Interchangeable Angelina Contour Cup Matte Beige
Body (HTML):
THIS ITEM IS NOT ELIGIBLE FOR FREE RETURNS & EXCHANGES!! 

*You may return or exchange this item by sending it back to us & emailing us shop@thebralab.com

Please use the size guide shown below to convert your size to our Bra Lab sizing.

Newly improved for maximum fit and comfort, our signature design Angelina Cup is a full coverage, contour molded cup with light foam padding and underwire that provides maximum support and shaping. 

  • Dual Side Closures to Fine Tune Fit
  • Use with Interchangeable Back Straps
  • Multi-Way Shoulder Strap Loops on Interior of Cup
  • Strapless, Cross Back, Classic, Halter, One Strap, Double Criss Cross, and Many More!

Not sure which bra to get? For general questions send us an email to shop@thebralab.com

Model 1 is typically a 30DDD and she is wearing size C with a Medium (30-34) back strap. Model 2 is wearing a B cup with a Medium (30-34) back strap. Model 3 is wearing a C cup with a Small (26-30) back strap.

Cup based off of a 36 band size. 

Material: Nylon Spandex

Care: Hand Wash

Patented Design
